    General Stores in Kandivali West, Mumbai

    General Stores in Kandivali West, Mumbai

    Commonly known as 'kiranas' in the local parlance, mom-n-pop shops are nothing but general stores. There's bound to be a general shop located at every other corner of any neighbourhood. As general stores, these establishments store items categorised as food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. These shops and establishments are a part of the distributor network of FMCG brands and companies selling a wide range of products. General store products comprise of food grains, pulses, household items, toiletries, cosmetics, biscuits and packaged food items, bakery products, confectionery items, and local foods. Following the traditional system, most serve customers through a counter system, certain stores encourage self-service for their customers, by following a more modern system. Aiming for the convenience of the locals, these general stores also offer complimentary doorstep delivery services. Please scroll up to find a list of General Stores in Kandivali West, Mumbai.
